{"BRAKE":[{"def":"A fern of the genus Pteris, esp.","pos":""}],"BRAKEMAN":[{"def":"A man in charge of a brake or brakes.","pos":""},{"def":"The man in charge of the winding (or hoisting) engine for a mine.","pos":""}],"BRAKY":[{"def":"Full of brakes; abounding with brambles, shrubs, or ferns; rough; thorny.","pos":""}]}